{
  "name": "Elite Awareness",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/fleur-de-lis-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Skill </p><p>Prerequisite: Wisdom 20, Level 10+ </p><p>You have the wisdom associated with the most renowned masters of Ninshou, which grant you a level of awareness most others don't have.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• You gain a 1d4 bonus to all Wisdom saving throws you make.</p><p>• You gain Mastery in one Wisdom skill which you already have proficiency in.</p><p>• You gain a +5 bonus to your passive perception and Insight.</p><p>• You can use your action to try and gain an exalted perception into your current situation.</p><p> So long as you are not blind and/or deaf, all illusions, genjutsu with the Visual and/or Auditory keyword, and effects designed to deceive you, within the 60 feet of you, have their DC's reduced by 5 for the next minute, or until the start of your next turn if in combat.</p><p></p>",
